{"slug":"sirkuler-25-0071eng","reference":"Sirkuler_25_0071ENG","gazette":"Official Gazette Dated 31 December 2024 and Numbered 32769 3. Duplicate","title":"Changes have been made in the additional duties (IGV-EMY) for passenger cars originating in the People's Republic of China","date":"13 Ocak 2025","bodyHtml":"<p>With the amendment made in the annexes of<a href=\"https://www.resmigazete.gov.tr/eskiler/2024/12/20241231M3-1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration-line: underline; font-weight: bold;\"> the Decree Amending the Decision on the Application of Additional Customs Tax on Imports (Decision Number: 9392)</a>&nbsp; the application of additional financial obligations in passenger cars under tariff position 8703 has been changed.</p><p>With the amendment, the EMY rate/minimum amount for passenger cars originating in the People's Republic of China has been increased from 40%/ min.USD 7,000 to 50%/ min. USD 9,500.</p><p>Duty&nbsp; rates have not changed for hybrid vehicles that can be charged by connecting to an external power source and fully electric vehicles;</p><p>-40% in fully electric vehicles</p><p>-40%/ minimum&nbsp; USD 7,000 when charged by connecting to an external power source.</p><p>According to the Provisional Article of the Decision No. 9392, if the customs declaration for the import of the goods for which the additional financial obligation has been increased has been registered until 31/1/2025 (including this date), additional customs duty rates and/or additional financial obligation before 1/1/2025 will be applied.</p><p><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n <tbody><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;height:28.8pt\">\r\n  <td width=\"96\" nowrap=\"\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:72.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:28.8pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;<u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"64\" nowrap=\"\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:48.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:28.8pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;<u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"672\" colspan=\"2\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:504.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:28.8pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">IGV-EMY application in\r\n  passenger cars originating in the People's Republic of China<u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:1;height:14.4pt\">\r\n  <td width=\"96\" nowrap=\"\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:72.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">HS CODE</p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"64\" nowrap=\"\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:48.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">FOOTNOTE<u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"327\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:245.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">2024<u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"345\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:259.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">2025<u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:2;height:14.4pt\">\r\n  <td width=\"96\" nowrap=\"\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:72.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">870321101000<u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"64\" nowrap=\"\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:48.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">(16)<u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"327\" rowspan=\"27\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:245.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-align:justify\">40% / min.US $7,000/piece is applied as an additional\r\n  financial obligation. No additional financial obligation is applied to\r\n  imports made by benefiting from customs duty exemption within the scope of\r\n  the investment incentive certificate.<u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"345\" rowspan=\"27\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:259.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:14.4pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">50% / min. US$9,500/piece is applied as an additional financial obligation. No\r\n  additional financial obligation is applied to imports made by benefiting from\r\n  customs duty exemption within the scope of the investment incentive certificate.<u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:3;height:28.8pt\">\r\n  <td width=\"96\" nowrap=\"\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:72.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:28.8pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">870321901000<u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"64\" nowrap=\"\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width:48.0pt;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  mso-border-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:28.8pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\">(16)<u1:p></u1:p><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:4;hei